skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mount rainier
des:
Anyone in the Greater Seattle area can relate to the golden question: "Is the mountain out?"

This skill answers that question while supplying an image from the webcam on the Space Needle and the twitter post from @IsMtRainierOut.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
